  positioning = 'A managed deployment that takes your DevSecOps design from specification to a production-ready, security-embedded pipeline.',
  hero_summary = 'Implement your DevSecOps automation blueprint with structured configuration, integration testing, and a controlled handover that leaves your engineering teams operating a faster, more secure delivery pipeline from day one.',
  overview_paragraphs = '["The DevSecOps Automation Deploy service delivers configured, tested capabilities with structured integration, quality assurance, and handover to your operations team. This implementation delivers configured, tested capabilities with structured handover.","Implement agreed DevSecOps automation changes through managed configuration, integration, testing, and controlled launch support."]'::jsonb,
